Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.70,0:24:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to be a genius to display that or understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.32,0:24:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is truthful, integrous, and pro-life makes you go strong when I press down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.34,0:24:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is anti-life, poisonous, will kill you false, deceptive, and delusional,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.68,0:24:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,makes your arm go weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.20,0:24:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It does so despite what you might think.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.88,0:24:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,think about it so if i put a person's name in an envelope and i put another person's name in
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.66,0:24:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,another envelope now i don't tell the person i say it's a blind test what's in this envelope
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.54,0:25:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is the name of somebody who calibrates over 200 their arm goes really weak then i take the other
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.88,0:25:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,envelope i say the name of this person calibrates over 200 and they go strong and i open it up
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.33,0:25:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and the one that made them go weak which we've done many times
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.67,0:25:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,is karl marx just the name alone puts you down and jesus christ puts you up you know it's a very
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.33,0:25:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,simple test you have to have an iq over at least 40 or 50 to get it anybody doesn't get it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.22,0:25:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,people who have an
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.24,0:25:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,indignation
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.31,0:25:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,people who have an indignation
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.34,0:25:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,vested interest in falsehood
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.36,0:25:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,get very upset with this
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.50,0:25:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,test and have done everything they can to
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.30,0:25:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,discredit it and
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.62,0:25:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,vilify it
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.06,0:25:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,say that it's all trickery
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.22,0:25:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and stage magic and all that
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.08,0:25:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but we've done it many many
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.30,0:25:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,times many audiences
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.04,0:25:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,over decades and the results
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.22,0:25:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,are always the same
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.40,0:26:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,if I hold Abraham Lincoln
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.12,0:26:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in my mind and I say what am I holding
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.08,0:26:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in mind she goes strong
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.48,0:26:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,if I hold Adolf Hitler in my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.98,0:26:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I say what I'm holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.38,0:26:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates over 200 she goes weak
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.94,0:26:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,now I didn't tell her what I'm holding in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.31,0:26:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,how would she know
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.16,0:26:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to tell her
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.40,0:26:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,because she might cheat on me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.07,0:26:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,cheat
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.42,0:26:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,now I wouldn't trust it
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.96,0:26:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,just because of the sure suggestion
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.92,0:26:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,of it so if what
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.05,0:26:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hold in mind is over 200
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.00,0:26:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I say to her
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.81,0:26:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,what I'm holding in mind is over 200
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.98,0:26:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I get a yes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.00,0:26:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,or a no
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.75,0:26:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,we've done this probably close to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.61,0:26:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,10,000 times
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.03,0:26:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we've done it over 8,000 times
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.27,0:26:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,let's see
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.77,0:26:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we've done it over 8,000 times
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.13,0:26:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,7,500
