Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.03,0:58:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,96.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.03,0:58:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.03,0:58:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,96.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.03,0:58:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.03,0:58:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that say?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.03,0:58:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's 96 there?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.03,0:58:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.03,0:58:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.03,0:58:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.03,0:58:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,96.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.03,0:58:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.03,0:58:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.03,0:58:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost to where we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.03,0:58:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if we keep going in the direction we're going,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.03,0:58:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to end up where we're headed for.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.03,0:58:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.03,0:58:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose holy company.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.03,0:58:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice Socrates' view.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.03,0:58:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,See others as programmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.03,0:58:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.03,0:58:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So here's what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.03,0:58:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We become loving towards all of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.03,0:58:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,grateful for all that we have,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.03,0:58:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and benevolent.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.03,0:59:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So benevolence is an attitude in which we are gracious
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.03,0:59:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,towards all of life and all of its creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.03,0:59:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Benevolence, then, is a way of looking at the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.03,0:59:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,One can also be benevolent towards oneself,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.03,0:59:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to be benevolent towards oneself,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.03,0:59:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to be merciful towards oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.03,0:59:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,People are safer to be with who are merciful towards
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.03,0:59:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,themselves because vicious people,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.03,0:59:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,what they do is they project it outward onto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.03,0:59:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.03,0:59:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So unless a person is kind to themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.03,0:59:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,learns how to be kind to themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.03,0:59:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,they're not really safe to be with
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.03,0:59:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,because that can turn on you any second.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.03,0:59:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So we want to teach people to be easygoing with themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.03,0:59:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to be accepting of your own limitations
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.03,0:59:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,without going into guilt and self-hatred,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.03,0:59:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,without becoming self-punitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.03,0:59:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to be kindly towards oneself.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.03,0:59:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be kindly towards others
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.03,1:00:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're not kindly towards yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.03,1:00:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go through the gestures of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.03,1:00:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're not really being it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.03,1:00:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So being it means that what you would wish for others,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.03,1:00:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you now wish and employ towards yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.03,1:00:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You talk about being kind and understanding
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.03,1:00:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and helpful to others.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.03,1:00:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what's important is that you be that way to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.03,1:00:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone here kind and loving
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.03,1:00:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and benevolent towards themselves?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.03,1:00:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.03,1:00:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody hate yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.03,1:00:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo, I hate anybody who hates himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.03,1:00:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to kill anybody who hates himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.03,1:00:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want any...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.03,1:00:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so being benevolent and compassionate
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.03,1:00:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,towards all of life and all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.03,1:00:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,To be compassionate towards all of life
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.03,1:00:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of its expressions,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.03,1:01:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,including its expression as you,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.03,1:01:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,then is the very heart and source
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.03,1:01:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of a spiritual life.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.03,1:01:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a spiritual erudition, see,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.03,1:01:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,which does not require any book.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.03,1:01:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It merely realizes
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.03,1:01:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the kindness towards yourself and towards others
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.03,1:01:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is what uplifts mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.03,1:01:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Because as you...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.03,1:01:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The way you uplift mankind,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.03,1:01:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,people say, what can I do to help mankind?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.03,1:01:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What you can do is to be
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.03,1:01:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the highest being you can be,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.03,1:01:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to be as kind and considerate towards all of life
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.03,1:01:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.03,1:01:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, the beauty of all exists.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.03,1:01:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things have to be displayed,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.03,1:01:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,like these flowers,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.03,1:01:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so stunning, so stunning,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.03,1:01:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,before you finally see it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.03,1:01:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But then after a while,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.03,1:01:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you see it in every living thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.03,1:01:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You see it in every tree.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.03,1:01:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think we've asked this question before.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.03,1:01:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.03,1:01:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see if I have this question.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.03,1:01:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this question.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.03,1:02:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.03,1:02:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Every living thing is aware of the divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.03,1:02:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,of your existence as you walk by, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.03,1:02:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Every living thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.03,1:02:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,every tree,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.03,1:02:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,all the grass,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.03,1:02:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,all living things are aware
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.03,1:02:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that you have walked by.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.03,1:02:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.03,1:02:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, just to be
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.03,1:02:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and to be in what you are
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.03,1:02:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,uplifts the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.03,1:02:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to run out there
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.03,1:02:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and sign up for pledges for things.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.03,1:02:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You just be what you are
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.03,1:02:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to the fullest capacity.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.03,1:02:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Appreciate with joy
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.03,1:02:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,your own existence,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.03,1:02:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,your own creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.03,1:02:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We thank thee, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.03,1:02:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for our existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.03,1:02:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We thank you for our creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.03,1:02:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,By being thankful for our own creation,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.03,1:02:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,we bless all of creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.03,1:03:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.03,1:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll stop there for now,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.03,1:03:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll take a break.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.03,1:03:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And when do we resume?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.03,1:03:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We resume about 11.30.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.03,1:03:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.03,1:03:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,11.30.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.03,1:03:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,11.30.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.03,1:03:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We have refreshments
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.03,1:03:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,across the courtyard here.
